{"tid":548764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貨車甩孖轆擊中私家車","createTime":"2018-02-03T02:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T05:50:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c91a1016cef99ec096f07f037c7d5c1b58cf5a66","tid":548764,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20293853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293853&d=xIgoi0qI1Uh9wtwXt3H%2FzzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=95bb4099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293853&h=7103b8e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20293853</a><br />\n<br />\n貨車甩孖轆擊中私家車<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n<br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】一輛貨車昨於西貢公路行駛期間，左尾孖轆先後飛脫，撞向路邊咪錶及一輛途經私家車，私家車司機頸部受傷送院，警方正調查甩轆意外起因。<br />\n<br />\n現場為西貢公路雙線雙程車路，據目擊者陳先生表示，昨日下午1時許，他乘坐友人私家車尾隨涉事貨車沿上址往九龍，至白沙灣對開時，前車的左尾孖轆先後飛脫，分別撞毀路邊咪錶柱及彈向對面行車線一輛私家車車頭蓋，私家車司機大驚立即停車。陳先生指私家車司機自行離開車廂報警：「擋風玻璃都爛咗，如果打正啲可能成塊玻璃爛晒，車轆就打入車廂！」<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，59歲姓張私家車司機在意外中傷頸送院；53歲姓譚貨車司機稱事前由荃灣駕車到西貢進行工程，完工後離開西貢，未料車轆甩脫，經檢查發現有多口拴緊車轆的螺絲帽不翼而飛，未知原因，警方事後拖走貨車調查甩轆原因。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180203/large/a0704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2Fa0704a.gif&h=fb4a1092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貨車行駛期間孖轆飛脫（箭嘴示）。"},{"pid":"4d0f7c1a8bff30a4351dc7fa70e46733fc1fe8cc","tid":548764,"uid":3773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180203/large/a0704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2Fa0704a.gif&h=fb4a1092&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/170563410/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F170563410%2Foriginal.gif&h=a7de1cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f11f2f263107e0395189a5b3802cd694aff14f9","tid":548764,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1886da9a0b94f1059b55f790d284a3d2e752506f","tid":548764,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0f7c1a8bff30a4351dc7fa70e46733fc1fe8cc","tid":548764,"uid":3773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180203/large/a0704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2Fa0704a.gif&h=fb4a1092&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/170563410/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F170563410%2Foriginal.gif&h=a7de1cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}